spx.av

Class OpType

  • java.lang.Object
    • spx.av.OpType

  • public class OpType
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains constants that match the enumeration values of the SPxAVOpType enum from SPxAVCommon.h and functions to convert an op type to a string.
